pros:
1) technical tasks are challenging. great place to learn how to scale system, team formation, code base structure and apps;
2) salary package with guaranteed annual bonus, is above average Hong Kong, Taiwan and Singapore technical companies;
3) teammates are smart, nice and open to new technologies. lots of technical knowledge sharing day to day;
4) amazingly low turnover in tech team;

cons:
not really cons, but not good enough.
1) product growth targets are ambitious and projects are overwhelming in order to catch up the market and user base. however, whole company is trying to restructure regularly in order to improve communication and delivery efficiency;
2) the company grew so fast in past years that system are becoming legacy. need better ways and people to improve sustainability;
